MANIFOLD

A framework for a non-blocking server.

    Issues and Tasks: http://blogometer.com/trac/incubator
    Source: http://github.com/bigeasy/manifold/tree/master
    Contact: alan@blogometer.com

    Notes: http://delicious.com/alan/nio

PURPOSE

Manifold is the basis of an IMAP and SMTP server.

MOTIVATION

Created a shared server framework for two mail server applications.
